    Serializable, Comparable<PooledObjectState>

    public enum PooledObjectState
extends Enum<PooledObjectState>
    Provides the possible states that a PooledObject may be in.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.0

    • 枚举常量概要

      枚举常量 
      枚举常量和说明
      ABANDONED
      Deemed abandoned, to be invalidated.
      ALLOCATED
      In use.
      EVICTION
      In the queue, currently being tested for possible eviction.
      EVICTION_RETURN_TO_HEAD
      Not in the queue, currently being tested for possible eviction.
      IDLE
      In the queue, not in use.
      INVALID
      Failed maintenance (e.g. eviction test or validation) and will be / has been destroyed
      RETURNING
      Returning to the pool.
      VALIDATION
      In the queue, currently being validated.
      VALIDATION_PREALLOCATED
      Not in queue, currently being validated.
      VALIDATION_RETURN_TO_HEAD
      Not in queue, currently being validated.

    • 枚举常量详细资料

      • IDLE

        public static final PooledObjectState IDLE
        In the queue, not in use.

      • ALLOCATED

        public static final PooledObjectState ALLOCATED
        In use.

      • EVICTION

        public static final PooledObjectState EVICTION
        In the queue, currently being tested for possible eviction.

      • EVICTION_RETURN_TO_HEAD

        public static final PooledObjectState EVICTION_RETURN_TO_HEAD
        Not in the queue, currently being tested for possible eviction. An attempt to borrow the object was made while being tested which removed it from the queue. It should be returned to the head of the queue once eviction testing completes. TODO: Consider allocating object and ignoring the result of the eviction test.

      • VALIDATION

        public static final PooledObjectState VALIDATION
        In the queue, currently being validated.

      • VALIDATION_PREALLOCATED

        public static final PooledObjectState VALIDATION_PREALLOCATED
        Not in queue, currently being validated. The object was borrowed while being validated and since testOnBorrow was configured, it was removed from the queue and pre-allocated. It should be allocated once validation completes.

      • VALIDATION_RETURN_TO_HEAD

        public static final PooledObjectState VALIDATION_RETURN_TO_HEAD
        Not in queue, currently being validated. An attempt to borrow the object was made while previously being tested for eviction which removed it from the queue. It should be returned to the head of the queue once validation completes.

      • INVALID

        public static final PooledObjectState INVALID
        Failed maintenance (e.g. eviction test or validation) and will be / has been destroyed

      • ABANDONED

        public static final PooledObjectState ABANDONED
        Deemed abandoned, to be invalidated.

      • RETURNING

        public static final PooledObjectState RETURNING
        Returning to the pool.
